A Chinese man has been jailed for 11 years for cutting off his nine-year-old stepson's hand with a meat cleaver and boiling it so it would be impossible for surgeons to reattach.

Wang Xinyu, 31, met the boy's mother Xiao Shen just over a year ago and the pair had been looking at buying a flat together in Shenyang - a city in east China's Liaoning province.

But after the couple had a furious telephone argument about money, Wang lost his temper and began beating Xiao Jun with a stick before cutting off his hand with a meat cleaver and throwing it into a pot of boiling water that was being used to cook their evening meal.

